I established the Matt Grey Design type foundry in 2010 with the aim of producing modern and versatile typefaces with an array of different styles.

Sales through Gumroad are direct and will always be the cheapest option, followed by Fontspring. Feel free to contact me to ask for a discount.

For a preview playground of the fonts listed, visit MyFonts
